8
[p 
	"…or 
	[b 
		""Why I Think This Movie Should Be Published."
	]b
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This is a list of the most popular excuses to accept/publish a run, received from the peers at 
	[a href=/forum 
		"TASVideos forum boards
	]a
	", compiled and analysed by 
	(__wikiLink|user:moozooh)
	".
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Discussion takes place 
	[b 
		[a href=/forum/t/5743 
			"here
		]a
	]b
	".
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Disclaimer
	$LF
	[a id=heading-276 
	]a
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		" This list is meant to be only half-serious and reflect the opinion of its creator, who encourages everyone to take it lightly. It doesn't aim to represent the views of other users, including administration members, in any way. It does aim to represent the importance of the site's 
		(__wikiLink|MovieRules)
		" and 
		(__wikiLink|Guidelines)
		", though.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" This list isn't meant to make fun of judges' decisions; rather of the reasons some viewers give for why the judges should accept & publish a certain movie. The author sees it as a handy document that can be used to solve difficult situations and arguments, complementary to 
		(__wikiLink|judge guidelines)
		".
		$LF
	]li
]ul
